  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      582.92,
      555.17,
      738.31
    ],
    "text": "Tonight: Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, North-western, Southern and Uva provinces and in Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts. Mainly dry weather will prevail over the other parts of the island. Tomorrow: Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central, Southern, North-western and Uva provinces and in Ampara, Batticaloa and Anuradhapura districts after 2.00 p.m.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      741.37,
      555.05,
      776.23
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy falls above 50 mm are likely at some places in Western and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Kandy, Nuwara-Eliya, Galle and Matara districts.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      3.119999885559082,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      779.29,
      378.93,
      798.55
    ],
    "text": "Mainly dry weather will prevail over the other parts of the island.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      801.85,
      555.17,
      839.38
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa and Uva provinces and in Galle and Matara districts during the early hours of the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      842.44,
      554.36,
      878.74
    ],
    "text": "The general public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      881.8,
      555.12,
      951.72
    ],
    "text": "On the apparent northward relative motion of the sun, it is going to be directly over the latitudes of Sri Lanka during 05th to 15th of April in this year. The nearest areas of Sri Lanka over which the sun is overhead tomorrow (12th) are Cheddikulam, Kebithigollewa, Gomarankadawala and Nilaveli about 12:11 noon.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      7.920000076293945,
      12.0
    ]
  },
